---
title: BBQ-Style Chicken Breasts Dinner with Potato Salad and Garlic Broccoli
description: If you're craving some BBQ but don't want to head outside to fire up the grill, we've got you covered! This dish delivers the joys of a backyard BBQ sesh, but it all happens in the kitchen in under 30 minutes.
